Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that a channeled teaching is necessarily negative. It may well be positive.\NYou should know who is it, you know, what is the level of truth of the consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:01:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because many people go into, ooh, ah, it's the old Master Baba Dung Dong,\Nand, you know, you go, what is the energy of Master Ding Dong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think of a very famous Baba right now.\NWe have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baba I'm thinking about, it calibrates over 200,\Nnow over 300, over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to calibrate over 200.\NSo we discover new things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We discover new things all the time.\NMany of the so-called, many of the sort of legendary spiritual teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of them are all in India or somewhere in a foreign place or some foreign culture or some foreign time,\Nwhen you calibrate their energy, it's really negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes you weak, you know.\NAnd you don't want to upset your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't do that.\NYou don't want to tell them about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always recommend, what you should do is go through your spiritual library.\NEverybody here probably has as many books at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And all those that make you go strong, you put over on this side of the room,\Nand all those that make you go weak, you put them on that side of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a profound experience.\NAnd you realize some things that you never realized before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.\NAll of a sudden you get where spiritual falsehood comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from erroneous context.\NBecause a lot of the gurus are very slick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met some of the slickest.\NThey know the right things to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have enough spiritual truth in their bag of tricks that they can convince anybody.\NAnd the reason you can't detect it, because what's out is the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the context is out of your range of awareness.\NAnd you're not spiritually advanced enough, the third eye isn't open,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can see the context out of which the other speaker is speaking.\NSo you don't get what the error is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because the error is outside your,\Noutside your vision, you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So being able to calibrate, being able to discern the level of truth,\Nis very, very, very practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It can help you find lost objects,\Nand it can save your lifetimes of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because following a false guru,\Nand then discovering disillusionment at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,can be exquisitely painful.\NExquisitely, it's probably more painful than losing a loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing a child, I've lost children.\NLosing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,being a spiritual rake is probably the most painful of all human,\Npossible human experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That you've been misled by some guru,\Nthat you've given up everything for in worship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and believed everything he said to Zoe as a god.\NYou know, because there are teachings like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to make your guru into like a god-like figure,\Nand surrender to your guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you find out he's been ripping you off.\NIt's really, really savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've seen some patients,\NI saw one, it took her six pros act a day to hold back the suicidal depression
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that was precipitated when she realized that\Nthe person that she thought was, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,her sacred guru on earth was just, you know,\Ntaking her for a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, his heart chakra was negative.\NWell, the words were all correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it didn't come out of India.\NIt's a nature and tradition in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Americans are very naive.\NA slick guru, guru-ism, comes out of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slick evolution.\NThousands of years of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're more clever than you are.\NEverything you can think of, they've already thought about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple thousand years ago and took care of it.\NThere's no way your intellect is going to discern it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Without kundalini-ology, I don't know how anybody can protect himself.\NAnd the spiritual rationalizations are so clever and so intriguing and so seductive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:05:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's the seduction of false spiritual glamour\Nthat is the track to the average spiritual seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've come across.\NWe've all done all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all studied Reiki.\NAnd we've gone to these workshops and those workshops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've followed Master so-and-so.\NWe got channelings from so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And psychic readings.\NAnd the magic dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And what else have we done, right?\NThe magic mantras and the cards and all the deal, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everybody in finding out what is spiritual truth,\Nit's a normal thing to check out what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's labeled spiritual, right?\NSpiritual readings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they must be spiritual, right?\NSo, there's Madam so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's got Master so-and-so on the other side.\NAnd she sees that, hmm, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you sit there and your ears are just perked up\Nbecause you're just sure there's some great wisdom of the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that's about to be laid on you as a gift.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NIf you can calibrate the level of truth of the speaker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is on the other side,\Nthen you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe.\NI don't care how many readings you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you know the calibration of the channeler\Nand that which is being channeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NSo, she reminded me that the world runs on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, quarter to 12.\NI don't know what our time schedule is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to start at 1230, I think.\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NWe're going to run from 10 to 1230.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NShe distracted reality in this world for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.\NI wouldn't know where I was if it weren't for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to her this morning, I don't know where I am.\NShe said, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NIf I'm going to speak someplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly I feel like this energy comes on.\NIt's like a huge deep breath suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the presence intensifies\Nand there's a feeling of an incredible joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's hard to know where you are in the world\Nand where you're supposed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you're measuring and all those things.\NAnyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those are the kind of phenomena that happened.\NI just thought you would do the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there was, besides the Kundalini positive energy,\Nthere was very intense spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,something else also,\Nbecause it was almost as though
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as you reach a certain level of consciousness,\Nyou pull up its opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was also years of clearing\Nwhat's out in the human consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,not in my own personal self or karmic background.\NBut there was years of,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of clearing that which is out in the collective of mankind.\NAnd there was a great deal of physical pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a great deal of the nervous systems,\Nvery often wracked with extreme pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,considerable pain,\Nuntil that particular dilemma was worked through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that used to worry me until,\NI remember the Buddha said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said that he had years\Nin which his body was wracked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as though his bone,\Neven his bones ached.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And Susan pointed that out.\NShe said, look at the good ones then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.\NSo, there are various physical phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that go with this intense spiritual work.\NI like the Course in Miracles extremely much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now we'll resume.\NWhat time do we resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what time do we resume?\N1.30?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to quit from 12.30 to 1.30.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk more about\Nthe Course in Miracles this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I, at one time, taught it.\NI brought it to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew Helen, of course,\Nand the psychologist that she worked with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who died of heart problems, etc.\NAnd so, I have a profound interest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Course in Miracles.\NAnd an understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what we were talking about this morning,\Nsort of gives it the concept
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the conceptual context\Nin which to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the Course in Miracles.\NHow it is that to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit for a miracle,\Nto ask to see it as it is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,all you're really asking for\Nis to move from perception to vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're really saying is\Nif I get out of an arbitrary positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the entire picture is revealed to me,\NI'll see that there is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to be solved\Nbecause there isn't any problem to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that out of the wholeness,\Nthe oneness, the wholeness of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then, vision prevails over perception.\NMiracles are only miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of the ego.\NFrom the viewpoint of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,they're only the way things are.\NThere's nothing miraculous about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You think of a certain thing\Nand then when you get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it is that,\Nbut that's the way it is in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But to the person who spends every day\Nin Newtonian paradigm of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they would term many of these things miraculous.\NMiraculous became commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the way things work.\NWhat you hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the nice things about that,\Nknowing this too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is that\Nyou see on the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that all the\Nthings that calibrate below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all the negativity,\Nanger, resentment, self-pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things,\Nwell, the calibrated number
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is the logarithm of a relative power.\NSo you see that hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,where is hatred on here?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred.\NHatred is way down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And fear.\NAll these things that are like 100 or less,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,well,\Nwhat we worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is our negative thoughts and feelings,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritually driven people\Nare usually bugged by
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what they consider their problems,\Nis things that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,\Nyou get a resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel bad about it,\Nyou feel angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel bad about it,\Nyou get into self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything negative we feel bad about\Nbecause we're trying to evolve beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?\NSo we know we're in some kind of an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So not only do you feel guilty\Nthat you're guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but you feel guilty\Nthat you're feeling guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're guilty,\Nyou understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was seeing things correctly,\NI wouldn't be feeling guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so I must be screwed up.\NSo now you're guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,about feeling guilty\Nabout being guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you see what I'm saying?\NSo spiritual people really have,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,really a problem\Nthat other people don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They just feel guilty\Nin the hell with you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and they enjoy it.\NHatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or something,\Nmakes you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Ntired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They get,\Nthey like it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't like it anymore.\NNow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think,\NGod,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,\NGod,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,\NLord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Holy Spirit\Nto see this differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they see this\Nas in truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?\NNot that he's a hateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,evil person\Nthat I want to get even with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Nwe worry about our negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,\Nbut you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from the consciousness level here,\Ndon't forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,these are all logarithmic.\NLove is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NBut we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the log 500,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So a negative thought\Nis,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,well,\NI don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people\Nin the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,think that\Na negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is so weak and puny\Nthat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly,\Ndon't quote me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but you could spend all day\Nthinking negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even worry about it.\NHave one loving thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,love your kitty,\Nsay,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sweetie pie,\NI adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're God's little\Ngifting mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And,\Nman,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you just outdid\Nall that negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Nnow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if that wasn't so,\Nwhen you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world's\Npopulation
